{"tid":1622512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Be humble?","createTime":"2019-10-04T16:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T16:32:59.000Z","uid":313039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c2fd7fa9ad4b4fd17317eb075305e5b5b856212c","tid":1622512,"uid":313039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:28:48.000Z","msg":"姐係車緊人放學 望住rb 大家都辛苦我明呀<br />\n但我地都想快啲送多啲人返學<br />\n好對唔住 係我對唔住你地搬開rb<br />\n開返條線比我地載人返去<br />\n但係唔該比返我地應有既素質<br />\n唔好一黎話人又狗又乜 <br />\n我地都係想幫手足們早啲返去休息備戰。<br />\n<br />\n真係好對唔住呀柴灣手足<br />\n但真心 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be Humble</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外街上面真係仲有好多人需要你地做校車呀 真係好多人返唔到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盡做！"},{"pid":"92d5294271aaa81d582c39b6243515e1a0b8022c","tid":1622512,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人唔會用素質</span></span>"},{"pid":"927d835521e514dbf0552f5af21b420c90d22dbb","tid":1622512,"uid":313039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"真心發夢左咁耐<br />\n咁樣比手足話心都淡埋"},{"pid":"85c2952244c42d0329c4a3e807936954235c21fc","tid":1622512,"uid":313039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92d5294271aaa81d582c39b6243515e1a0b8022c","tid":1622512,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人唔會用素質</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:32:59.000Z","msg":"Sor 諗唔到用乜字 請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}